  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"id-1.19.2-UpdatesandEnhancements\">Updates and Enhancements</h3><ul><li><p>The Ticket Item Search widget has been moved back to the right side of the page.</p></li><li><p>The PAX A920 device is now compatible with <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934295157/Integrated+Payment+Processing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934295157\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments.</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.19.2-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>A UI bug affecting the device history of a repair device has been fixed.</p></li><li><p>A bug affecting Swedish characters for imports/exports has been fixed.</p></li></ul>",
